---
// Composant Hero pour la page d'accueil
---

<section class="hero">
	<div class="hero-content">
		<h1 class="hero-title">Horizon Slavia</h1>
		<p class="hero-subtitle">Parcourez les sentiers des légendes oubliées</p>
		<p class="hero-description">
			Découvrez l'Europe de l'Est à travers ses mythes ancestraux, ses langues fascinantes
			et ses paysages enchanteurs. Un voyage au cœur de la culture slave.
		</p>
		<div class="hero-cta">
			<a href="/legendes" class="cta-primary">Découvrir les légendes</a>
			<a href="/europe-centrale" class="cta-secondary">Explorer la région</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.hero {
		background: transparent;
		color: white;
		padding-inline: 2rem;
		padding-block-start: 6rem;
		padding-block-end: 6rem;
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		margin-block-start: 0;
		min-height: calc(100vh - 5rem);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.hero-content {
		max-width: 100vw;
		margin: 0 auto;
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.hero-title {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #e0e7ff 100%);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-clip: text;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.hero-subtitle {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
		color: #e0e7ff;
		font-style: italic;
	}

	.hero-description {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin: 0 0 3rem 0;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
		max-width: 700px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.hero-cta {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	.cta-primary,
	.cta-secondary {
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 8px;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		display: inline-block;
	}

	.cta-primary {
		background: var(--accent);
		color: white;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(35, 55, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.cta-primary:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(35, 55, 255, 0.4);
	}

	.cta-secondary {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		color: white;
		border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
		backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
	}

	.cta-secondary:hover {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
		border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.hero {
			padding-inline: 1.5rem;
			padding-block-start: 6rem;
			padding-block-end: 4rem;
			margin-block-start: 0;
		}

		.hero-title {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.hero-subtitle {
			font-size: 1.125rem;
		}

		.hero-description {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		.hero-cta {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: stretch;
		}

		.cta-primary,
		.cta-secondary {
			width: 100%;
		}
	}
</style>
